Teaching from my new Arabic texbook:
“Step-By-Step Arabic Language” by Nisreen Neqresh Beshqoy

From my experience in teaching Arabic for college students in the US I created this textbook, it teaches Modern Standard Arabic (MSA), taught and used in all Arab countries.

This book is for the independent learners, it includes a pronunciation system to help you master the material without any assistance.

Available for purchase. Just go to the link on my profile. Or you can ask your local bookstore to order it from IngramSpark, which is an international book distributor.
